ida. Male Monastery. Abbot Anastasie.\n\n===Vicariate for the Orthodox Christian Communities of Slavic Tradition===\n* [[St. Nicholas Monastery (Fort Myers, Florida)|St. Nicholas Monastery]] [http://floridamonastery.org/pastyrskoe-slovo-arhimandrita-aleksandra-k-prihozhanam-voskresene-13-oktyabrya-2019-g/] [https://www.goarch.org/-/2020-03-09-vicariate-of-slavic-churches]\n\n==Greek Orthodox Old Traditional==\nSee [[Greek Old Calendarists]], as they are not part of [[Eastern Orthodox Church|Orthodox Church]].\n\n===Male===\n* [[Holy Ascension Monastery|Monastery of the Holy Ascension]], Woodstock, New York.  Metropolitan Demetrios. [http://www.ascensionmonastery.org]\n* St. Gregory Palamas Monastery, Etna, California.  Abbot Akakios.\n* [[Holy Cross Monastery (Niagara Falls, New York)|Holy Cross Monastery]], Niagara Falls, New York. Archimandrite Nicholas (Iuhos). [http://www.holycross-niagarafalls.org] (Synod in Resistance)\n* [http://saintbarbaramonastery.org Monastery of Saint Barbara], Middletown, New Jersey. [http://saintbarbaramonastery.org]\n*[[Holy Transfiguration Monastery (Brookline, MA)|Holy Transfiguration Greek Orthodox Monastery]], Brookline, Massachusetts.  Abbot Isaac. [http://www.thehtm.org/]\n\n===Female===\n*Saint Syncletike Monastery, Farmingdale, New York.  Metropolitan Pavlos. [http://thenunsgarden.org]\n\n==Moscow Patriarchate==\n\n===Patriarchal parishes in the United States===\n*[[The Monastery of St. Mary of Egypt (New York City, New York)|The Monastery of St. Mary of Egypt]] (Mercy House), New York City, New York.  Igumen Joachim.\n**[[Holy Trinity Monastery (Baltimore, Maryland)|Holy Trinity Monastery]], Baltimore, Maryland.  Dependency of The Monastery of St. Mary of Egypt.\n\n===Russian Orthodox Church Outside Russia===\n\n====Male====\n* [[Holy Trinity Monastery (Jordanville, New York)|Holy Trinity Monastery]], [[Jordanville, New York|Jordanville]], [[New York (state)|New York]].\n* [[Holy Cross Monastery (Wayne, West Virginia)|Hermita